l stimuli, accelerates gastric emptying, and reduces contractions of the gallbladder and phasic contractions of sphincter of Oddi [L873, A19702]. At higher concentrations, pinaverium also exhibits very weak anticholinergic effects [L873] but is not shown to display vasodilatory or anti-arrythmic actions [T37]. ', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
